jei.mountains_poem.item_8: It can remove the unformed paper from the papermaking table, after which it can be placed on the drying table to dry as papers.

jei.mountains_poem.item_6: A plant commonly found in the Underworld that can be used to make Under Flower Mooncakes.
jei.mountains_poem.item_1: A salad made from a crimson fungus that can be used to mutate xuan tortoises by feeding them.
jei.mountains_poem.item_5:
It can be used to store xuan tortoise shells that express the intent of the sacrifice (which determines the attributes of the gods you summon), as well as meat and jade sacrifices.
The first row of slots is used to store meat offerings, the second row is to be used for jade offerings on the left, and the right is to be placed for sacrificial xuan tortoise shells.
jei.mountains_poem.item_4: A tasty meat product that can be eaten as is, or placed in a suitable place for eating or dipping when player sneaking.
jei.mountains_poem.item_3: A liquid made by soaking trees or other plants that can be smelted in a furnace to turn into paper pulp.
jei.mountains_poem.item_2: A leather with magical powers, which can be obtained by killing boyi.
